            "</ul>"
            "<p><b>Overall score formula:</b> 0.35 × Completeness + 0.25 × Uniqueness + "
            "0.20 × Consistency + 0.20 × Validity. Completeness is weighted highest because missing "
            "data affects nearly every analysis method.</p>"
