            "<li><b>Skewness</b> -- Is the distribution symmetric (≈0), right-skewed (>0), or "
            "left-skewed (<0)?</li>"
            "<li><b>Kurtosis</b> -- Are the tails heavy (>0) or light (<0) compared to a normal distribution?</li>"
            "</ul>"
            "<p><b>For categorical columns:</b> count, unique, top (most frequent), freq (frequency of top).</p>"
            "<p><b>Beginner tip:</b> Look for columns where mean and median are very different -- "
            "this signals outliers or skewed data that may need special treatment.</p>"
